casebody.data:
177 A.3d 124 ATLANTIC AMBULANCE CORPORATION, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. JOHN G. CULLUM AND MARY CLARE COLLUM, DEFENDANT-MOVANTS; ATLANTIC AMBULANCE CORPORATION, PLAINTIFF, v. HALA HITTI AND ANTOINE HITTI, DEFENDANTS.

M-455/456/457 September Term 2017

079804 December 13, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to impound the record (M-457) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motions to expand the record (M-456) and for leave to appeal (M-455) are denied.
